                      </tr><tr>
                        <th> </th><th>12</th><td class="r"><span>== Quick Install a Released Version ==</span> </td>
                      </tr><tr>
                        <th> </th><th>13</th><td class="r"><span>For a quick install, first make sure you have [http://python.org/download Python] (2.3-2.6) and [http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/EasyInstall#installing-easy-install easy_install].</span> </td>
                      </tr><tr>
